tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
stu_tags: LOTS OF HOMEWORK  CARING  ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS
comments: Assignment every week both creative and applicable. All are called papers, but some are short answer types that are under a page. Very accessible. I texted, called her, and sent inbox messages to her on the World classroom portal. Gave good feedback when given. If not given, I asked and received it. I learned a lot as I had no business background.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: She makes u work but it\'s worth it. She\'s pretty fair.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: The course information had a tendency to be dry and somewhat boring, but Kimra made it more interesting through lecture and discussion. Very understanding and worked to make sure we got the most out of the class. I\'d highly recommend this class. It was challenging, but overall rewarding.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: Great teacher- real life examples. Engaging and open-minded. During class we disagreed on economic concepts(She works for the US government concerning trade; I come from an Austrian-Economic background which views public governing entities less efficient that private firms) we did find common ground and accept my opinions. No book; got an A.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: I found this gal to be one of the WORST professors I\'ve ever had. I think primarily because she shouldn\'t teach online classes. Assignment instructions were about as clear as MUD! Took forever to grade papers and respond to emails, which is KEY in online learning. I would not recommend this one AT ALL. I think classmates would concur.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: Great Professor, very engaging, intelligent, and funny.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: There is quite a bit of reading, the tests can be a little rough, but speak up during class and you will be fine. Her personality will win you over, and she is always open to suggestions if the reading is unbearable.

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  LOTS OF HOMEWORK (1)  Caring (1)
comments: I had Kimra for an International business class. She was extremely nice and helpful. She had an awesome sense of humor too. She expects you to come prepared for class: Read the cases, text, current news etc. Do your work and participate and you will do fine! There is a written case due every other week and a final test. She respects every student!
